title: GR_50K
name: GR_50K
description:
10km by 10km grid created using EEA fishnet tool in ETRS 89 LAEA 52 10 projection. The grid was clipped to a 20km buffer of the country extent- the country extent was based on using the data from EEAMapdata_5210_v2_3.  The table file attached associated with the document contains the starting point (the "0, 0 point") for the grid for each country along with the number of rows and columns used in the fishnet tool.  It should be noted that this generates a grid to that extent and will need to be edited to the extent of the country in question. 
http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gis/geographicinformationstandards.html
